raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Naomi: Hey all!
Naomi: Congratulations on everyone for completing the first week's tasks!
Naomi: Caleb especially took on some heavy lifting
Mabel: That's true! 🤭
Naomi: So I decided to throw a little welcome party this weekend
Naomi: I don't think we all got a chance to mingle properly
Paige: Finally, something fun
Paige: I was getting super bored on weekends
Paige: img: paige/11
Naomi: 😅
Naomi: Anyway, the party is going to be on Sunday and we'll have drinks!
Naomi: We'll play some of our old club games since we're big enough to now
Player: What kind of games?
Naomi: I'm glad you asked
Naomi: All sorts!
Naomi: One of my personal favorites is the dark room game 🤭
Caleb: Oh.. that game 😳
Mabel: What's that? 🤔
Caleb: 🙉
Naomi: It's a little party game me and Caleb cooked up
Naomi: One participant goes into the photography dark room
Naomi: and the rest of us vote on one of the others to go in to kiss that person 
Mabel: Kiss!?
Player: Wow 😆
Naomi: Mhmm!
Naomi: Naturally so the first person doesn't know who their partner is
Naomi: But that makes the kiss more exciting doesn't it? 😊
Naomi: We'll make sure everyone gets a chance
Naomi: Oh and we might take a silhouette shot too 😉📷
Paige: Sounds like my kinda game 😌
Mabel: What kinda game is that 🙊
Naomi: Are you coming as well?
Player: Yeah why not
Mabel: B-babe!!
Naomi: What do you think Mabel? 🤭
Naomi: You in?
Mabel: I mean if everyone else is going... then I guess I should too 🙈
Mabel: What do you think babe
- It'll be fun!
	Player: It'll be fun
	Naomi: It's always fun!
	Mabel: If you say so..
- You don't have to come
	Player: You don't have to come
	Player: If you think it won't be fun
	Paige: Yeah, listen to your boyfriend 😘
	Mabel: Hey!! 😤
Mabel: Then I'm totally coming
Mabel: img: mabel/141
Player: 😁
if Story.has_flag(\"JasonRt\")
	Player: Would you mind if I invite my friend, Naomi?
	Naomi: Not at all, it's an open party!
	Player: Awesome!
	Mabel: Is that the friend you've been talking about?
	Mabel: The one you met on the first week? 🤔
	Player: Yeah!
	Player: I think you and him would get along
	Player: He knows a lot about you 😄
	Mabel: Omg that makes me so nervous 🫢
	Mabel: I hope you said good things 👀
	Player: The best things
	Player: He's excited to meet you
	Mabel: Yay, I am too 🥰🥳
	do queue_social_post(\"jason_party_hype\")
else:
	- [Invite Jason]
		do queue_social_post(\"jason_party_hype\")
		Player: Would you mind if I invite my friend, Naomi?
		Naomi: Not at all, it's an open party!
		Player: Awesome!
		Mabel: Is that the friend you've been talking about?
		Mabel: The one you met on the first week? 🤔
		Player: Yeah!
		- I think Naomi would like him [if Story.red_heart >= 3]
			set Story.flag = \"JasonNaomiEvent\"
			Player: I think Naomi would like him
			Naomi: Got me on your mind, do ya? 🤭
			Naomi: Or are you trying to ship me with this mysterious boy 😏
			Player: No comment! 🙂
			Naomi: img: naomi/25
			Naomi: If he's your friend, he's gotta be some one interesting hehe
			Naomi: I'll give him a chance 😉
		- I think Paige would get along with him [if Story.blue_heart >= 3]
			set Story.flag = \"JasonPaigeEvent\"
			Player: I think Paige would get along with him
			Paige: You really think you know all about me after our one \"photography session\" huh 🙂‍↔️
			Paige: You that confident?
			Player: Maybe 🙂
			Paige: img: paige/12
			Paige: I'll be there to totally party, like everyone else
			Paige: And boys that give me attention are the ones that get my attention
		- He's a fun guy!
			Player: He's a fun guy!
			Naomi: Neato, he's welcome!
	- [Don't invite Jason]
		Player: Is anyone else coming?
Mabel: Maybe I should invite Nina 🤔
Paige: NINA??
Paige: No way, don't you dare invite that cruel gremlin 😡
Mabel: Eep.
Mabel: Okay, sorry!
Paige: Not your fault, she's just an annoying person 🙄
Naomi: Ladies, lets not invite conflict okay?
Naomi: Prioritize our club members' feelings!
Mabel: Sowwy Naomi 🥺
Naomi: Don't worry sweetie ❤️
Player: Is Alice coming?
Naomi: Probably not, she doesn't mesh well with parties she said
Alice: Sorry.
Mabel: Don't worry Alice!
Mabel: I hope you can come next time!
Alice: Uhm..
if Story.white_heart >= 2:
	Player: I hope so too
	Alice: Thank you 😊
Naomi: It was a nice chat everyone, hopefully we have a high turnout and a lot of fun this Sunday!
Mabel: Can't wait!
Caleb: Same
Paige: Finally
Player: Exciting
Naomi: Ciao everyone!
do social_post(\"naomi_party_announce\")
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
